divs: Sighting DetailsAs i was sitting in my backyard filming the full moon, i observed two ufo's fly pass the full moon less then 6 seconds. i noticed the unidentified objects from the corner of my eye when i looked down at the camcorder's screen. When i looked at the recording i was stunned of what i saw and couldn't believe what i had caught on film. The first ufo flew passed at high speeds and it kinda wobbled in a straight slanted line and at the same time turning upside down and then downside up. The second ufo dropped down like a tear drop at high speeds and it had like an American Eagle shape to it at one point. I felt so stunned at first to spot something pass the moon so fast and through my camcorder. I immediately went to show my girlfriend and friends right after i caught it on film. After the sighting, i began my research on my laptop and watched the video over 100 times to finally come to a conclunsion that these were U.F.O.'s
Summary: two U.F.O's fly pass the moon at high speeds
